            "raw_kind": "footnote",
            "raw_text": "1\n\nI. N. Bronshtein, K. A. Semendyayev, and K. A. Hirsch (Eng.\ntrans. Ed.), Handbook of Mathematics, New York, Van Nostrand\nReinhold Co., 1985, pg. 720.",
